text: Cheng Lim LRT Station is an LRT station in Sengkang, Singapore. ==Timeline== *1 January 2013 The station opened. *2018 Sengkang General and Community Hospital opens. It is connected to the station. ==Sources== ==Other websites== *SBS Transit Website Category:Sengkang Category:Light Rail Transit (Singapore) stations
